---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Corporate Fleet"
  description="Weyland-Yutani operates one of the largest private spacecraft fleets in existence -- over 10,000 registered vessels servicing 47 star systems. Exploration, colony transport, freight, military support, and research."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          FLEET OPERATIONS DIVISION
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-none uppercase">
          CORPORATE<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">FLEET</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-4xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          THE LARGEST PRIVATE SPACECRAFT FLEET IN HUMAN HISTORY
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">10,000+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">REGISTERED VESSELS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">47</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">STAR SYSTEMS SERVICED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">2034</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">FTL-CAPABLE SINCE</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">FLEET OPERATIONS</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              OVERVIEW
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6">
              CONNECTING <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">WORLDS</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> WEYLAND-YUTANI OPERATES ONE OF THE LARGEST PRIVATE SPACECRAFT FLEETS IN EXISTENCE. FROM SINGLE-CREW SURVEY SHIPS TO KILOMETER-LONG COLONY VESSELS, OUR FLEET REPRESENTS THE BACKBONE OF INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE, EXPLORATION, AND COLONIZATION.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> SINCE THE LAUNCH OF THE USCSS HELIADES IN 2034 -- THE FIRST FASTER-THAN-LIGHT SPACECRAFT -- WEYLAND-YUTANI HAS CONTINUOUSLY EXPANDED AND MODERNIZED ITS FLEET. TODAY, OVER 10,000 REGISTERED VESSELS OPERATE ACROSS 47 STAR SYSTEMS, CARRYING COLONISTS, CARGO, SCIENTIFIC EXPEDITIONS, AND SECURITY FORCES.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> FLEET MANAGEMENT IS COORDINATED FROM THE LUNA CONSTRUCTION YARDS AND ORBITAL ASSEMBLY PLATFORMS, WHERE VESSELS ARE DESIGNED, BUILT, COMMISSIONED, AND MAINTAINED. THE FLEET OPERATIONS DIVISION MANAGES ALL LOGISTICS, SCHEDULING, CREWING, AND MAINTENANCE ACROSS THE ENTIRE NETWORK.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> EVERY VESSEL IN THE FLEET IS EQUIPPED WITH WEYLAND-YUTANI PROPRIETARY SYSTEMS: FTL DRIVES, MU-TH-UR OR WALTER-SERIES OPERATING SYSTEMS, HYPERSLEEP MODULES, AND ADVANCED NAVIGATION. THESE INTEGRATED TECHNOLOGIES ENSURE FLEET-WIDE STANDARDIZATION AND OPERATIONAL RELIABILITY.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE FLEET SERVES AS THE ESSENTIAL LINK BETWEEN EARTH, LUNA, AND EVERY COLONY WORLD IN EXISTENCE. WITHOUT IT, INTERSTELLAR CIVILIZATION WOULD BE IMPOSSIBLE. EACH VESSEL DEPARTURE CARRIES THE MATERIALS, PERSONNEL, AND RESOURCES THAT SUSTAIN HUMAN EXPANSION ACROSS THE STARS.
              </p>
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold border-l-4 border-[#FFC600] pl-4">
                "THE CORPORATE FLEET IS NOT MERELY A TRANSPORTATION NETWORK. IT IS THE CIRCULATORY SYSTEM OF INTERSTELLAR CIVILIZATION."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fleet Categories -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            FLEET CLASSIFICATION
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            VESSEL <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CATEGORIES</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Exploration -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">EX</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">EXPLORATION VESSELS</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">DEEP SPACE SURVEY & DISCOVERY</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              LONG-RANGE EXPLORATION AND SURVEY CRAFT DESIGNED FOR INDEPENDENT DEEP SPACE OPERATIONS. EQUIPPED WITH ADVANCED SENSOR ARRAYS, GEOLOGICAL SURVEY SYSTEMS, AND EXTENDED-DURATION LIFE SUPPORT. THESE VESSELS CHART NEW SYSTEMS AND IDENTIFY VIABLE COLONY CANDIDATES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Colony Ships -->
          <a href="/fleet/covenant-class" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">CS</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">COLONY SHIPS</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">LONG-RANGE COLONIZATION</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              MASSIVE VESSELS DESIGNED TO TRANSPORT THOUSANDS OF COLONISTS IN HYPERSLEEP ACROSS INTERSTELLAR DISTANCES. INTEGRATED TERRAFORMING MODULES, EMBRYO STORAGE, AND AUTONOMOUS NAVIGATION FOR DECADE-LONG VOYAGES TO FRONTIER WORLDS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COVENANT-CLASS <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Freight/Transport -->
          <a href="/fleet/nostromo-class" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">FT</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">FREIGHT & TRANSPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">COMMERCIAL TOWING & CARGO</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE BACKBONE OF INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE. COMMERCIAL TOWING VEHICLES, AUTOMATED ORE HAULERS, AND BULK FREIGHT TRANSPORTS MOVE MILLIONS OF METRIC TONS OF CARGO ANNUALLY BETWEEN COLONY WORLDS, MINING OPERATIONS, AND EARTH.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW NOSTROMO-CLASS <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Military Support -->
          <a href="/fleet/conestoga-class" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">MS</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">MILITARY SUPPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">SECURITY & FORCE PROJECTION</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              LIGHT ASSAULT STARSHIPS AND ESCORT VESSELS PROVIDING SECURITY INFRASTRUCTURE FOR COLONIAL INVESTMENTS. BUILT UNDER CONTRACT FOR THE UNITED AMERICAS ALLIED COMMAND, THESE VESSELS CARRY COLONIAL MARINE DETACHMENTS AND RAPID DEPLOYMENT ASSETS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW CONESTOGA-CLASS <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Research -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">RV</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">RESEARCH VESSELS</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">SCIENTIFIC & CORPORATE R&D</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              DEDICATED SCIENTIFIC PLATFORMS FOR BIOLOGICAL, GEOLOGICAL, AND ASTRONOMICAL RESEARCH IN THE FIELD. EQUIPPED WITH FULL LABORATORY SUITES, SPECIMEN CONTAINMENT, AND ADVANCED ANALYSIS SYSTEMS. MANY OPERATE UNDER RESTRICTED ACCESS PROTOCOLS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Heritage -->
          <a href="/fleet/heliades" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">HV</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">HERITAGE VESSEL</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">USCSS HELIADES -- FIRST FTL</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE HISTORIC FIRST FASTER-THAN-LIGHT SPACECRAFT, LAUNCHED IN 2034. NOW PRESERVED AS A CORPORATE HERITAGE ARTIFACT AND SYMBOL OF WEYLAND-YUTANI'S PIONEERING LEGACY IN INTERSTELLAR TRAVEL.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW HELIADES <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Shipyard Information -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              CONSTRUCTION
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              SHIPYARD <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">OPERATIONS</span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">LUNA CONSTRUCTION YARDS</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
                THE PRIMARY SPACECRAFT MANUFACTURING COMPLEX, LOCATED AT LUNA COLONY. TWELVE ORBITAL DRYDOCKS CAPABLE OF SIMULTANEOUSLY CONSTRUCTING VESSELS UP TO 1,500 METERS IN LENGTH. ANNUAL OUTPUT EXCEEDS 200 MAJOR VESSELS AND 2,000 AUXILIARY CRAFT.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">DRYDOCKS</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">12 ORBITAL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">MAX VESSEL LENGTH</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">1,500M</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">ANNUAL OUTPUT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">200+ MAJOR VESSELS</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">ORBITAL ASSEMBLY PLATFORMS</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
                SUPPLEMENTARY CONSTRUCTION AND REFIT FACILITIES DISTRIBUTED ACROSS KEY TRANSIT NODES. THESE PLATFORMS HANDLE VESSEL MAINTENANCE, RETROFIT, EMERGENCY REPAIR, AND COMPONENT PRE-ASSEMBLY. CRITICAL TO MAINTAINING FLEET READINESS AND OPERATIONAL TEMPO.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">PLATFORMS</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">28 ACTIVE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">LOCATIONS</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">14 STAR SYSTEMS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs">SERVICES</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs">REFIT / REPAIR / ASSEMBLY</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fleet Management -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="terminal max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="terminal-content">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">&gt; FLEET MANAGEMENT</h2>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
              THE FLEET OPERATIONS DIVISION COORDINATES ALL VESSEL SCHEDULING, CREWING, MAINTENANCE, AND LOGISTICS FROM THE LUNA OPERATIONS CENTER. REAL-TIME FLEET TRACKING ACROSS ALL 47 STAR SYSTEMS ENSURES OPTIMAL RESOURCE ALLOCATION, ROUTE EFFICIENCY, AND RAPID RESPONSE TO OPERATIONAL REQUIREMENTS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
              <a href="/colonies" class="btn-primary">COLONY OPERATIONS</a>
              <a href="/careers" class="btn-secondary">FLEET CAREERS</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
